column2: JDWP: Ignore vmVersion number when attached to dalvik/Art

column3:
This number is somewhat meaningless on android and varies based on the
android version. It should be ignored and the values returned by
VirtualMachine.Capabilities and VirtualMachine.CapabilitiesNew should
be considered the sole source of truth.
merged into master, thanks for your contribution!
